sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant GraphApp as Look Graph Webview
participant GraphRouter as GraphMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as GraphDataUseCase
participant Repository as GitRepository implements RepositoryOperationCapabilities
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime

User->>GraphApp: Open Look Graph
GraphApp->>GraphRouter: graph/dataRequest(repositoryLocator, PageRequest, filters, requestId)
GraphRouter->>Registry: resolveRepository(repositoryLocator)
Registry-->>GraphRouter: GitRepository
GraphRouter->>UseCase: getGraphData(Repository, filters, PageRequest, signal)
par Commit graph
  UseCase->>Repository: getCommitGraph(filters, PageRequest, signal)
  Repository->>Runtime: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, PageRequest, signal)
  Runtime->>Cli: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, PageRequest, signal)
and Branches and tags
  UseCase->>Repository: listBranches(signal)
  Repository->>Runtime: listBranches(executionContext, signal)
  Runtime->>Cli: listBranches(executionContext, signal)
  UseCase->>Repository: listTags(signal)
  Repository->>Runtime: listTags(executionContext, signal)
  Runtime->>Cli: listTags(executionContext, signal)
and Worktrees and submodules
  UseCase->>Repository: listWorktrees(signal)
  Repository->>Runtime: listWorktrees(executionContext, signal)
  Runtime->>Cli: listWorktrees(executionContext, signal)
  UseCase->>Repository: listSubmodules(signal)
  Repository->>Runtime: listSubmodules(executionContext, signal)
  Runtime->>Cli: listSubmodules(executionContext, signal)
end
Cli-->>Runtime: graph domain values
Runtime-->>Repository: graph domain values
Repository-->>UseCase: graph domain values
UseCase-->>GraphRouter: GraphData
GraphRouter-->>GraphApp: graph/dataResponse(requestId, GraphData)
GraphApp-->>User: Render graph rows, branches, tags, worktrees, submodules

User->>GraphApp: Select initialized submodule repository
GraphApp->>GraphRouter: graph/dataRequest(submoduleRepositoryLocator, PageRequest, filters, requestId)
GraphRouter->>Registry: resolveRepository(submoduleRepositoryLocator)
Registry-->>GraphRouter: GitRepository for initialized submodule
GraphRouter->>UseCase: getGraphData(Repository, filters, PageRequest, signal)
UseCase->>Repository: getCommitGraph(filters, PageRequest, signal)
Repository->>Runtime: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, PageRequest, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, PageRequest, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: Page(GitCommit)
Runtime-->>Repository: Page(GitCommit)
Repository-->>UseCase: Page(GitCommit)
UseCase-->>GraphRouter: GraphData
GraphRouter-->>GraphApp: graph/dataResponse(requestId, GraphData)
GraphApp-->>User: Render submodule graph

alt Git watcher requests auto-refresh
  GraphRouter-->>GraphApp: graph/refreshRequested
  GraphApp->>GraphRouter: graph/dataRequest(repositoryLocator, CurrentCursorPageRequest, filters, requestId)
  GraphRouter->>Registry: resolveRepository(repositoryLocator)
  Registry-->>GraphRouter: GitRepository
  GraphRouter->>UseCase: getGraphData(Repository, filters, CurrentCursorPageRequest, signal)
  UseCase->>Repository: getCommitGraph(filters, CurrentCursorPageRequest, signal)
  Repository->>Runtime: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, CurrentCursorPageRequest, signal)
  Runtime->>Cli: getCommitGraph(executionContext, filters, CurrentCursorPageRequest, signal)
  Cli-->>Runtime: Page(GitCommit)
  Runtime-->>Repository: Page(GitCommit)
  Repository-->>UseCase: Page(GitCommit)
  UseCase-->>GraphRouter: GraphData
  GraphRouter-->>GraphApp: graph/dataResponse(requestId, GraphData)
  GraphApp->>GraphApp: Reduce only if graph data changed
  GraphApp-->>User: Preserve stable UI when unchanged
end
